Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.40,0:14:36.44,Main,Guitar Man,0,0,0,swipe,{\pos(1040,1005)}Biar kujelaskan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.44,0:14:36.47,Main,Guitar Man,0,0,0,swipe,{\pos(1200,1005)}Biar kujelaskan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.48,0:14:36.52,Main,Guitar Man,0,0,0,swipe,{\pos(1545,1005)}Biar kujelaskan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.52,0:14:36.56,Main,Guitar Man,0,0,0,swipe,{\pos(2060,1005)}Biar kujelaskan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.96,0:14:41.13,Main,Guitar Man,0,0,0,,Dalam suatu band, sangat penting untuk\Nmenyelaraskan dengan personel lain!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.13,0:14:43.94,Main,Guitar Man,0,0,0,,Tapi, Hitori yang memiliki kecemasan\Nsosial dan selalu menunduk,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.94,0:14:45.67,Main,Guitar Man,0,0,0,,dia punya kecenderungan\Nuntuk menahan diri!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.32,0:14:48.03,Main,Guitar Man,0,0,0,,Mungkin dia pemain solo yang jago,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.03,0:14:51.74,Main,Guitar Man,0,0,0,,tapi saat di band, hierarkinya\Nlebih rendah dibanding kutu air!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.01,0:14:54.28,Main,Hitori,0,0,0,,Salam kenal.\NAku Plankton Gotoh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.28,0:14:57.08,Main,Nijika,0,0,0,,Dia terdengar seperti komedian garing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.32,0:14:59.71,Main,Hitori,0,0,0,,{\i1}Lalu, Gotoh Hitori pun\Nberubah menjadi abu,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.71,0:15:02.96,Main,Hitori,0,0,0,,{\i1}dan tidak akan menyentuh gitar lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.41,0:15:11.01,Main,Nijika,0,0,0,,{\an8}Lah, bentar-tar-tar-tar!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.45,0:15:12.76,Main,Nijika,0,0,0,,Hei! Keluar, dong!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.00,0:15:14.60,Main,Nijika,0,0,0,,Bentar lagi konsernya mau dimulai, lo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.60,0:15:16.52,Main,Hitori,0,0,0,,Ya-Ya-Yah, aku enggak bisa!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.52,0:15:19.18,Main,Nijika,0,0,0,,Kan kamu baru pertama kali main, nih!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.18,0:15:21.44,Main,Nijika,0,0,0,,Apa boleh buat?\NKita kan band dadakan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.44,0:15:22.77,Main,Ryo,0,0,0,,Aku sih jago.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.23,0:15:26.36,Main,Nijika,0,0,0,,Pokoknya, lihat ke sini dulu!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.36,0:15:28.14,Main,Nijika,0,0,0,,Kembali ke kenyataan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.99,0:15:32.68,Main,Hitori,0,0,0,,Aku juga enggak bisa membuka\Nacara dan sebagainya ....
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.68,0:15:36.57,Main,Hitori,0,0,0,,A-Ah! Mungkin aku bisa\Nmelakukan harakiri pas konser!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.57,0:15:39.49,Main,Hitori,0,0,0,,Se-Seenggaknya, mereka bisa\Nmengingat nama bandnya, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.49,0:15:40.88,Main,Hitori,0,0,0,,Maaf, aku ampas!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.88,0:15:41.92,Main,Nijika,0,0,0,,Itu terlalu rok, ancrit!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.30,0:15:43.45,Main,Ryo,0,0,0,,Tenang saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.45,0:15:47.13,Main,Ryo,0,0,0,,Kalau penonton menyorakimu,\Nakan kupukul mereka dengan basku.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.13,0:15:50.68,Main,Hitori,0,0,0,,Me-Memangnya, bas bisa\Nmengeluarkan suara selembut itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.68,0:15:52.72,Main,Nijika,0,0,0,,Pertumpahan darah termasuk rok, sih.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.72,0:15:53.63,Main,Ryo,0,0,0,,Justru karena rok, coy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.63,0:15:55.73,Main,Hitori,0,0,0,,Jangan dikaitkan dengan\N"rok" semua, dong!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.73,0:16:00.17,Main,Nijika,0,0,0,,Lagipula, yang bakal nonton konser kita,\Npaling cuma teman-temanku saja, kok!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.99,0:16:03.63,Main,Ryo,0,0,0,,Temanku hanya Nijika doang.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.63,0:16:07.72,Main,Nijika,0,0,0,,Cewek SMA biasa mana tahu\Nmusik yang bagus atau enggak.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.72,0:16:10.03,Main,Hitori,0,0,0,,{\i1}Komentar begitu biasanya\Nbakalan drama di internet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.60,0:16:12.73,Main,Nijika,0,0,0,,Ya? Jadi gak usah cemas!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.15,0:16:14.76,Main,Hitori,0,0,0,,Meski kamu bilang begitu juga ....
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.76,0:16:16.55,Main,Ryo,0,0,0,,Aku tahu musik yang bagus, kok.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.55,0:16:18.17,Main,Nijika,0,0,0,,Kamu mah udah gila, Ryo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.61,0:16:21.54,Main,Nijika,0,0,0,,Jangan nyengir, heh.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.76,0:16:23.14,Main,Hitori,0,0,0,,Maaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.59,0:16:24.72,Main,Nijika,0,0,0,,Tapi ....
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.72,0:16:26.46,Main,Ryo,0,0,0,,Jangan memaksanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.76,0:16:29.06,Main,Nijika,0,0,0,,Iya juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.06,0:16:30.70,Main,Nijika,0,0,0,,Maaf karena sudah memaksamu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.70,0:16:32.17,Main,Hitori,0,0,0,,Ah, kalau itu ...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.97,0:16:37.05,Main,Hitori,0,0,0,,Ju-Justru aku senang\Nkalian mau mengajakku.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.70,0:16:40.60,Main,Hitori,0,0,0,,Dari dulu, aku ingin sekali masuk band ....
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.60,0:16:43.47,Main,Hitori,0,0,0,,Ta-Tapi, aku tidak bisa\Nmengumpulkan anggotanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.47,0:16:46.52,Main,Hitori,0,0,0,,Jadi, aku hanya mengunggah\Nvideo {\i1}cover{\i0} di internet saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.52,0:16:48.19,Main,Ryo,0,0,0,,Biasanya, kamu main lagu apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.19,0:16:51.23,Main,Hitori,0,0,0,,Su-Supaya aku bisa memainkannya\Nsaat band terbentuk,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.23,0:16:54.26,Main,Hitori,0,0,0,,biasanya aku meng-{\i1}cover{\i0} lagu\Ndari band yang populer tahun lalu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.26,0:16:54.99,Main,Nijika,0,0,0,,Eh? Gokil!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.28,0:16:56.80,Main,Hitori,0,0,0,,Yah, biasa aja, sih ....
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.80,0:16:59.38,Main,Hitori,0,0,0,,Ini bukti dampaknya.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.38,0:17:02.75,Main,Hitori,0,0,0,,Sepertinya, aku memang tidak cocok\Nmembentuk band dengan orang lain.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.13,0:17:05.36,Main,Nijika,0,0,0,,Meng-{\i1}cover{\i0} lagu populer?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.36,0:17:07.73,Main,Nijika,0,0,0,,Dia seperti {\i1}guitarhero{\i0}, deh!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.73,0:17:08.46,Main,Nijika,0,0,0,,Kamu tahu, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.92,0:17:11.63,Main,Nijika,0,0,0,,{\an8}Mungkin dia seumuran dengan kita.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.21,0:17:11.17,Main,Hitori,0,0,0,,{\i1}guitarhero{\i0} ....
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.63,0:17:12.99,Main,Hitori,0,0,0,,{\i1}Eh, maksudnya aku?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.99,0:17:15.56,Main,Nijika,0,0,0,,Kalau kamu gak tahu,\Nnanti kukirim pranalanya, deh!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.56,0:17:18.16,Main,Nijika,0,0,0,,Dia jago banget!\NKamu harus dengar, deh!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.16,0:17:20.08,Main,Hitori,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ja ... go?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.08,0:17:23.75,Main,Ryo,0,0,0,,Dia suka muncul di rekomendasiku,\Njadi aku pernah nonton.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.75,0:17:25.14,Main,Ryo,0,0,0,,Dia emang jago.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.14,0:17:26.04,Main,Nijika,0,0,0,,Kan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.04,0:17:27.94,Main,Nijika,0,0,0,,Tapi penamaannya jelek banget, deh.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.69,0:17:29.65,Main,Hitori,0,0,0,,{\i1}Iya, toh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.65,0:17:33.52,Main,Nijika,0,0,0,,Aku sudah mengikuti\Nsama nyalain loncengnya!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.52,0:17:35.78,Main,Nijika,0,0,0,,Suatu saat, aku ingin bermain dengannya!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.78,0:17:37.66,Main,Hitori,0,0,0,,{\i1}Barusan sudah, sih ....
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.08,0:17:41.28,Main,Nijika,0,0,0,,Intinya, yang mau aku bilang itu ....
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.28,0:17:44.77,Main,Nijika,0,0,0,,Orang-orang yang jago\Ndan populer di luar sana ...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.77,0:17:48.58,Main,Nijika,0,0,0,,... ada banyak yang bermain gitar,\Nmeski tidak ditonton siapa pun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.40,0:17:50.84,Main,Nijika,0,0,0,,Entar kamu coba tonton, deh!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.84,0:17:52.95,Main,Nijika,0,0,0,,Nanti kamu pasti paham maksudku!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.65,0:17:56.60,Main,Hitori,0,0,0,,{\i1}Selama ini, aku merasa kalau\Norang-orang di dunia nyata,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.60,0:18:00.01,Main,Hitori,0,0,0,,{\i1}tak ada satu pun yang peduli padaku ....
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.47,0:18:05.94,Main,Nijika,0,0,0,,Hanya karena kamu gagal hari ini,\Nbukan berarti menyerah begitu saja!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.94,0:18:08.29,Main,Nijika,0,0,0,,Bisa jadi kita yang gagal ....
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.29,0:18:09.00,Main,Ryo,0,0,0,,Kegagalan kita?{}{}{n: Potong jadi "Kita?" aja mungkin, CPSnya bang}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.94,0:18:11.09,Main,Nijika,0,0,0,,Hitori?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.09,0:18:14.78,Main,Hitori,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tapi, seseorang yang sangat\Nbaik ini selalu menontonku,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.78,0:18:17.17,Main,Hitori,0,0,0,,{\i1}dan mau berbicara denganku.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.17,0:18:18.24,Main,Ryo,0,0,0,,Oh, dia bangkit.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.74,0:18:22.16,Main,Hitori,0,0,0,,{\i1}Keajaiban ini mungkin\Nhanya sekali seumur hidup!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.87,0:18:24.82,Main,Hitori,0,0,0,,{\i1}Aku takkan menyia-nyiakannya!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.61,0:18:27.50,Main,Hitori,0,0,0,,E-Eng, aku ....
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.96,0:18:30.92,Main,Nijika,0,0,0,,Jangan-jangan,\Nkamu mau tampil di konser?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.33,0:18:34.42,Main,Nijika,0,0,0,,Hitori?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.42,0:18:36.32,Main,Hitori,0,0,0,,{\i1}Pikiranku bilang iya ....
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.32,0:18:37.82,Main,Hitori,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tapi, aku masih ketakutan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.82,0:18:40.39,Main,Hitori,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mustahil aku bisa tampil\Ndi hadapan banyak orang!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.64,0:18:43.33,Main,Ryo,0,0,0,,Kalau takut, kamu main sambil pakai ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.31,0:18:48.56,Main,Hitori,0,0,0,,Su-Suasananya sama seperti\Ntempat biasanya aku main gitar!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.20,0:18:51.19,Main,Nijika,0,0,0,,Kamu tinggal di mana, sih?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.63,0:18:54.64,Main,Hitori,0,0,0,,Ayo kita meriahkan\Nkonsernya, Shimo-Kita!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.64,0:18:56.15,Main,Ryo,0,0,0,,Tiba-tiba suaranya jadi lantang, dong.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.43,0:18:59.48,Main,Nijika,0,0,0,,Oh iya, nanti kamu\Nperkenalannya gimana?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.48,0:19:02.17,Main,Nijika,0,0,0,,Mau pakai nama asli, "Hitori"?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.17,0:19:03.90,Main,Hitori,0,0,0,,Y-Yah, kayaknya jangan ....
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.90,0:19:05.77,Main,Nijika,0,0,0,,Kamu ada nama panggilan gak?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.77,0:19:09.02,Main,Hitori,0,0,0,,Pa-Pas SMP, biasanya orang\Nmemanggilku "Anu" sama "Oi", gitu ....
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.02,0:19:10.84,Main,Nijika,0,0,0,,Itu mah bukan nama panggilan!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.84,0:19:14.79,Main,Hitori,0,0,0,,A-Ah, soalnya aku tidak pernah kenal dekat\Nsama orang buat dapat nama panggilan!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.00,0:19:16.22,Main,Ryo,0,0,0,,Hitori ....
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.22,0:19:17.94,Main,Ryo,0,0,0,,Hitoribocchi ....
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.94,0:19:19.12,Main,Ryo,0,0,0,,Gimana kalau Bocchi?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.12,0:19:21.18,Main,Nijika,0,0,0,,Ngomongnya gak pake mikir, ancrit!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.18,0:19:23.29,Main,Hitori,0,0,0,,A-A-Aku Bo-Bo-Bocchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.29,0:19:24.14,Main,Nijika,0,0,0,,Dia suka, toh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.40,0:19:26.18,Main,Hitori,0,0,0,,Tadi itu panggilan pertamaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.72,0:19:28.36,Main,Nijika,0,0,0,,Aku jadi berlinang air mata.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.36,0:19:31.03,Main,Hitori,0,0,0,,Ah, kamu belum\Nmemberitahuku nama bandnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.11,0:19:34.63,Main,Ryo,0,0,0,,Namanya Kessoku Band.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.03,0:19:39.02,Main,Hitori,0,0,0,,Kessoku Band ....
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.02,0:19:40.82,Main,Hitori,0,0,0,,Tali pengikat?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.75,0:19:42.57,Main,Ryo,0,0,0,,Muncrat!{}{}{n: kalo gk salah main pun si Ryo, entah kalo lu mo coba buat sama kyk lain sebelumnya}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.57,0:19:44.82,Main,Nijika,0,0,0,,Apa coba?!\NEntar kita ganti, ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.82,0:19:46.60,Main,Ryo,0,0,0,,Kenapa? Namanya bagus, lo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.60,0:19:47.81,Main,Hitori,0,0,0,,I-Iya.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.91,0:19:52.05,Main,Nijika,0,0,0,,Bahas namanya entar aja,\Nbentar lagi kita tampil, lo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.19,0:19:54.42,Main,Nijika,0,0,0,,Tenang!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.84,0:19:58.55,Main,Nijika,0,0,0,,Gapapa kalau ampas,\Nyang penting bikin asyik aja!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.55,0:20:01.26,Main,Nijika,0,0,0,,Karena perasaan itu penting\Ndalam bermain musik.
